Your poor heart must be
black-and-blue with bruises.

00:48:10.980 --> 00:48:12.650
How much...

00:48:12.650 --> 00:48:15.380
How much!

00:48:18.440 --> 00:48:20.500
Aigoo...

00:48:20.500 --> 00:48:22.860
Ho Suk.

00:48:22.860 --> 00:48:26.630
No, no. It's on me.

00:48:26.630 --> 00:48:29.890
I should've caught on sooner.

00:48:31.650 --> 00:48:37.120
I should've shared your emotional load.

00:48:38.270 --> 00:48:43.030
I'm thick as a brick. I'm sorry, Unni.

00:48:43.030 --> 00:48:46.170
No, don't be sorry.

00:48:46.170 --> 00:48:48.010
I'm the one who's sorry.

00:48:48.010 --> 00:48:50.100
I'm the bad one here.

00:48:50.100 --> 00:48:52.130
No. No.

00:48:52.130 --> 00:48:55.680
I'm the fool. I'm sorry.

00:48:55.680 --> 00:48:59.520
Hey, don't say that. I'm really sorry.

00:48:59.520 --> 00:49:01.330
How can you say that?

00:49:01.330 --> 00:49:03.060
I'll be back.

00:49:04.390 --> 00:49:07.030
Man, that's killer.

00:49:07.030 --> 00:49:09.370
That was funny.

00:49:09.370 --> 00:49:11.960
You said you'd crash here for a few days.

00:49:13.090 --> 00:49:15.230
Why aren't you leaving?

00:49:15.230 --> 00:49:17.500
How many days has it been now?

00:49:17.500 --> 00:49:19.200
I'm going.

00:49:19.200 --> 00:49:24.200
I will, but I need work
to earn cash for a flophouse.

00:49:24.200 --> 00:49:27.250
But there are no jobs. I keep striking out.

