♫ Saturday afternoon, don't hesitate like that ♫

01:15:10.030 --> 01:15:15.590
♫ Come dance with me ♫

01:15:15.590 --> 01:15:21.560
♫ I don't want to talk
about anything tiring today ♫

01:15:21.560 --> 01:15:27.020
♫ So let's dance, ah-hoo, ah-hoo ♫

01:15:27.020 --> 01:15:30.090
♫ The busy Monday ♫

01:15:30.090 --> 01:15:33.020
♫ The chaotic Tuesday ♫

01:15:33.020 --> 01:15:38.830
♫ The boring Wednesday are gone ♫

01:15:38.830 --> 01:15:41.700
♫ Saturdays are golden ♫

01:15:41.700 --> 01:15:44.610
♫ That's today ♫

01:15:44.610 --> 01:15:50.300
♫ So come dance with me ♫

01:16:04.160 --> 01:16:09.650
And that wraps up the performance
for the 1989 Miss Korea Preshow,

01:16:09.650 --> 01:16:11.640
where excitement and nerves coexist.

01:16:11.640 --> 01:16:15.340
Thank you for staying with us late into the night!

01:16:15.340 --> 01:16:16.800
Following tonight's Preshow,

01:16:16.800 --> 01:16:22.040
please look forward to tomorrow's
Miss Korea finals broadcast as well.

01:16:22.040 --> 01:16:23.980
Good night!

01:17:35.190 --> 01:17:40.650
♫ Call my name ♫

01:17:42.190 --> 01:17:47.700
♫ Break this silence ♫

01:17:47.700 --> 01:17:52.800
♫ So I don't fade into a darkness
that feels like forever ♫